&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OUR TEAM:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team is comprised of competent and caring resource professionals who are innovative, resourceful, collaborative, and helpful in facilitating the reentry process for the Offender Success Program of the Kinexus Group.  This responsibility requires that we be service oriented relative to the needs of all referred participants, while still assuring that all services adhere to Michigan Department of Corrections policies and procedures, financial requirements as established through the State funding source.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We lead by example by holding true to a high standard of excellence that drives positive Offender Success outcomes for successful reentry for returning citizens. The Department strives to be exemplary in all activities and to continuously exceed expectations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OUR DESIRED OUTCOMES:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
